<activity><title>Volume</title>
<introduction><p>You are designing a new coffee maker. The coffee filter must be 8.4 centimeters tall and shaped like a cone. The volume of the filter will therefore depend on how wide the opening is (the radius of the cone).</p></introduction>

<task><p>Write a formula for the filter's volume <m>V</m> in terms of its widest radius <m>r</m> (at the top of the filter). (Hint: Look up the formula for the volume of a cone.)</p>
<p>Simplify your formula by multiplying the constants together.</p></task>

