<activity><title>Extraction of Roots</title>

<task><p>Solve each equation by extraction of roots. <ol>
  <li><p><m>(x+3)^2=4</m></p></li>
  <li><p><m>(3x+1)^2=25</m></p></li></ol></p></task>

<task><p>Solve. Give your answers two ways: (i) exact values and (ii) approximations rounded to thousandths.<ol>
  <li><p><m>6(x-3)^2=30</m></p></li>
  <li><p><m>520+60(2+x)^2=1000</m></p></li></ol></p></task>

<task><p>Solve each formula for the requested variable.<ol>
  <li><p><m>V=\frac{1}{3}\pi r^2 h~~</m> for <m>r</m></p></li>
  <li><p><m>d=h-\frac{1}{2}gt^2~~</m> for <m>t</m></p></li></ol></p></task>
</activity>

